Procedure to register clients

the client logs into the system using their google account
then goes to associate policy screen
they are asked for a policy number
then their number phone for security purposes

once supplied correctly a notification is sent to the admin through the notifications console

the admin must then call the client and verify their policy by asking further security questions

then after allow access to the policy from the client side...

the client will be able to download and print their statements
able touse the referral system to promote midey funeral and earn an income


